<%= render 'layouts/nav' %>
<div class="submit-wrapper">
  <section class="header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <div class="service-box">
            <i class="fa fa-4x fa-paper-plane sr-icons"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <hr class="light">
          <h2 class="section-heading">Submit a Story</h2>
          <hr class="light">
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </section>

<div class="text">

  <p>If you are interested in contributing a story to Our Taiwanese American Story, read our <%= link_to 'Interview Guide', interview_guide_path%> for questions to help you get started.  Please note that by using this site and contributing your story, you are accepting our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.</p>

<p>Submissions can be in text, audio, or video format.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Written Submission: Please proofread for errors before submitting. Submissions are ideally 2000 words or fewer.</li>
  <li>Audio Submission: Upload your audio file to Soundcloud and submit the link below.</li>
  <li>Video Submission: If you have access to high quality video equipment, record a video of your story and upload it to Vimeo. Then submit the link to your video below.</li>
</ul>

<p>Once reviewed, your content will be posted on the website.  If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@ourtastory.com">info@ourtastory.com</a>.</p>
<%= render("form_submit_base") %>
</div>
</div>
